body.description: Huggies Natural Care Sensitive Baby Wipes are soft, plant-based wipes since 1990* (*70%+ by weight plant-based materials), made with 99% purified water and 1% skin essential ingredients for a gentle clean. Infused with aloe and vitamin E, the unique base sheet locks-in and absorbs the mess to help keep your baby's skin clean. With no harsh ingredients, Huggies Natural Care unscented diaper wipes are hypoallergenic, dermatologist-tested and pH-balanced to help maintain healthy skin for your baby. They're recognized by the National Eczema Association because they're safe for sensitive skin, being fragrance free, alcohol free, paraben free and do not contain phenoxyethanol or MIT. Huggies Natural Care unscented baby wipes are extra soft and gentle, making them ideal for sensitive newborn skin. These disposable baby wipes come in exclusive Winnie-the-Pooh packaging for a delightful touch. Plus, with EZ Pull 1-Handed Dispensing, it's easy to grab wipes without wasting sheets! With the #1 branded wipe**, you can feel confident you are giving baby a safe, gentle clean every time. (*70%+ by weight) (**Based on US Nielsen data ending 9/4/2021)

What makes Huggies Natural Care Sensitive Skin Baby Wipes right for you, baby? Designed to be gentle on sensitive skin, these wipes are made with 99% purified water and are enriched with aloe vera and vitamin E. They’re even accepted by the National Eczema Association! You’re learning all about new smells, baby, and you may want to know—are these wipes scented? Huggies Natural Care Sensitive Baby Wipes are hypoallergenic and free of fragrances, lotions, parabens and dyes. If you want a delicate scent, try our Natural Care Refreshing Baby Wipes or Nourish & Care Baby Wipes. Plants are things that grow, just like you, baby. But what does it mean that our wipes are plant-based? For your delicate skin, baby, we like to keep things simple. All of Huggies baby wipes are made with at least 70% plant-based fibers by weight to ensure a gentle clean that’s free of harsh chemicals. Are these wipes easy to grab one-handed? Mom’s got her hands full, baby. But don’t worry, our wipes have EZ Pull 1-Handed Dispensing so it’s easy to grab just one wipe at a time without wasting sheets. Using the toilet is an important lesson to learn, baby, but are Huggies Baby Wipes flushable? Designed for cushiony softness and durability, Huggies baby wipes don't easily break down after flushing. Please don’t flush baby wipes, and instead use the trash bin for your wipes and diapers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality and super dependable
reviews.reviewText: Huggies wipes have been used by me for my infant and have quickly become a family favourite. My baby's skin is quite fragile, and the wipes have never irritated or produced any redness. The perfect amount of softness and cleaning effectiveness is provided by the texture. The wipes are thick and strong, which I appreciate because they make changing diapers simple because they don't easily tear. The wipes are kept moist and fresh thanks to the handy packing. Overall, I have come to trust Huggies wipes as a dependable and gentle option for keeping my infant clean and at ease.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Our Household Essential - Huggies Natural Care Sensitive Baby Wipes
reviews.reviewText: Huggies Natural Care Sensitive Baby Wipes have become an indispensable part of our household. From my husband to my teen kids to our newborn, everyone swears by these wipes.What sets them apart is the superior feel and texture, which surpasses the competition. The wipes are gentle yet effective, making them ideal for a range of uses. Our newborn's delicate skin is well taken care of, and even our teen kids appreciate the quality.One unexpected bonus is that my husband has found a new use for them around the house. They are now his go-to for cleaning up chalk and other sticky substances. The versatility of these wipes has truly impressed us.The durability and effectiveness make Huggies Natural Care our preferred choice. We've tried others, but nothing quite matches up. As a family, we're sticking with these wipes for their reliability and overall excellence.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: "I've been using Huggies wipes for my little one, and they've quickly become a favorite in our household. The wipes are incredibly gentle on my baby's delicate skin and have never caused any irritation or redness. The texture is just right, providing effective cleaning while being soft to the touch. I appreciate the thickness and durability of the wipes; they don't tear easily, making diaper changes a breeze. The packaging is convenient and keeps the wipes moist, ensuring their freshness. Overall, Huggies wipes have earned my trust as a reliable and gentle option for keeping my baby clean and comfortable."

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not for us- but still great wipes for others preferences
reviews.reviewText: I got these bc Pampers wipes were out of stock and we’re only slightly disappointed. They are smaller than what we’re used to so I have to use more wipes with #2s. We also have a wipe warmer and have to reach in each time to grab them bc they separate too easily from one another instead of bringing the next one up. I think bc they aren’t as moist. They are however very durable and thick. Also, since they separate easier they do come out easier from the package it comes in. They also are pretty gentle on his bum.
